premise_source_doc_sentence: Ramzan Akhmadovich Kadyrov  (  -LSB- Рамза́н Ахма́тович Кады́ров , p = rɐˈmzan ɐxˈmadəvʲɪtɕ kɐˈdɨrəf -RSB- , Къадар Ахьмат-кIант Рамзан , Q̇adar Aẋmat-khant Ramzan born 5 October 1976  )  is the Head of the Chechen Republic and a former member of the Chechen independence movement .
Ramzan Kadyrov  (  born 1976  )  , head of Chechnya
